On ■■ month △ day, in the city of 〇〇, a boy named Yudai
Toyono (10 years old) died in a traffic accident while out
on an errand.

Yudai-kun was hit by a passenger car while on his way to buy
fruit at the supermarket for his mother's errand, and the
police are investigating the matter.

Additionally, his mother, Miwa Toyono, was found dead from
burns in their home on the same day, and the police are
looking into the suspicious deaths of both mother and child
on the same day--
